targets.rawSql:
SELECT
  date AS "time",
  fz_icu as "ICU Fallzahl",
  fz_icu_free + fz_icu as "ICU Kapazität"
FROM fallzahlen
WHERE
  $__timeFilter(date) AND bundesland = $bundesland
ORDER BY 1
